# monorepo version-file resolvers via `Extracted.appendWithSession` must
# keep the resolvers visible to the next-version write phase. Pre-fix,
# `tagReleasesPerProject.execute`'s `appendSessionSettings` rebuilt the
# structure from `mergeSettings` and dropped the hook overlay, so
# `set-next-versions` fell back to the default and silently overwrote
# `version.sbt`.
